| All requirements covered | 9/10 | All 8 required features mapped with traceability matrix; 3 nth-tier features assigned to deck. Minor: FR locale = UI strings only but nav shows [EN/ES/FR] toggle — slight mismatch with "multilingual" expectation unless explicitly scoped (it is, in plan). Contact form listed but no backend endpoint (static only) — acceptable given posting. |
