| Testing approach defined | 6/10 | Playwright WebGPU flags documented; mock fallback behavior defined for CI. But no test script outline, no assertion list, no component test plan. For richness=10 this is thin — deploy-test step will need to define assertions from scratch. Acceptable since deploy-test is a later node, but demo-builder should scaffold a minimal `e2e/` config. |
